%% DG-405: Dosya Yukleme Sequence Diyagrami
%% Durum: DRAFT
%% Editor: https://mermaid.live
%% Aciklama: Presigned URL ile guvenli dosya yukleme akisi
%% ---

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Client as Frontend
    participant API as API Server
    participant S3 as Object Storage<br/>(S3/GCS)
    participant Worker as Background Worker
    participant CDN as CDN

    Note over User, CDN: === Buyuk Dosya (Presigned URL) ===

    User->>Client: Dosya sec
    Client->>Client: Client-side validation (tip, boyut)
    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/upload/presign {fileName, fileType, fileSize}
    API->>API: Validate (tip whitelist, max boyut)
    API->>S3: Generate presigned PUT URL (15dk TTL)
    S3-->>API: {upload_url, file_key}
    API-->>Client: {uploadUrl, fileId, fileKey}

    Client->>S3: PUT dosya (dogrudan, backend'den gecmez)
    S3-->>Client: 200 OK

    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/upload/confirm {fileId}
    API->>S3: HEAD object (dosya var mi?)
    S3-->>API: 200 (var, boyut dogrulandi)
    API->>Worker: Queue: process_file {fileId, fileKey}
    API-->>Client: 200 {fileId, status: "processing"}

    Worker->>S3: Download original
    Worker->>Worker: Virus scan (ClamAV)
    Worker->>Worker: Resize (thumbnail, medium, large)
    Worker->>Worker: Convert to WebP
    Worker->>S3: Upload processed versions
    Worker->>API: Update DB record (urls, processed: true)

    Note over User, CDN: === Erisim ===
    User->>Client: Gorsel goruntule
    Client->>CDN: GET image URL
    CDN->>S3: Origin pull (ilk kez)
    S3-->>CDN: Image data
    CDN-->>Client: Image (cached)
